content.html:
Taken over a year to get a decent pic of a rifleman/titipounamu. NZ’s smallest bird, with the infuriating habits of hanging out in dense, dark forests and not sitting still. Luckily they’re outrageously cute…

#nzbirds #rifleman #titipounamu #birdphotography #birdsofmastodon #newzealandbirds

A discussion between Dr. Bashir and Garak of Star Trek: Deep Space Nine, illustrated with their photos.
Bashir: Do you think the rail workers should strike?
Garak: All exploited workers should strike!
Bashir: Even if it will disrupt the economy?
Garak: ESPECIALLY if it will disrupt the economy.
